e034cb16a9f12d0a58ab25a481d261d6a39a8c41.title: Hermitcraft 10: Episode 21 - NOSTALGIC
e034cb16a9f12d0a58ab25a481d261d6a39a8c41.description:
5 years ago to the day I build storage wars in Hermitcraft Season 6, and now I'm building storage containers in Hermitcraft season 10. The idea came to me at 3 o'clock in the morning, which is spooky. Clearly my brain is hard wired to think of storage wars on July 6th every half decade. I look forward to making another storage wars in 2029. 

In this episode we also blow up Hermticraft's magic mountain.
